'''标准阿尔及利亚柏柏尔语'''也可称为'''塔马齐格特语'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mae.gov.dz/FR2020054.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-22 |archive-date=2021-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101165520/http://www.mae.gov.dz/FR2020054.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是现代[[阿尔及利亚|阿尔及利亚]]使用的[[标准语|标准化]][[柏柏尔语|柏柏尔语]]，源自[[卡拜尔语|卡拜尔语]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.middleeasteye.net/columns/yennayer-between-politics-popular-celebration-and-invented-tradition-13552702|title=Algeria's Berber new year aims to show state's approval for 'invented tradition'|website=Middle East Eye|access-date=2021-01-22|archive-date=2019-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190128191220/https://www.middleeasteye.net/columns/yennayer-between-politics-popular-celebration-and-invented-tradition-13552702|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

柏柏尔语在2002年成为阿尔及利亚官方语言之一<ref name=chaker>{{cite journal |last1=Chaker |first1=Salem |title=Berber Challenge in Algeria: The State of the Question |journal=Jean Ait Belkhir, Race, Gender & Class Journal |date=2001 |volume=8 |issue=3 |pages=135–156 |jstor=41674987}}</ref>。许多标准化形式都是基于语言学家[[穆卢德·马梅里|穆卢德·马梅里]]（Mouloud Mammeri）的研究<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.huffpostmaghreb.com/2017/12/24/enseigner-tamazight-en-al_n_18906012.html|title=Le tamazight enseigné en Algérie est une "langue-monstre" que personne ne comprend|date=24 December 2017|website=Al HuffPost Maghreb|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227114436/https://www.huffpostmaghreb.com/2017/12/24/enseigner-tamazight-en-al_n_18906012.html|archive-date=27 February 2018}}</ref>。

